	<div class="panel panel-default">
		<div class="panel-heading">课程性质、目的和要求</div>
		<div class="panel-body">
<p>MATLAB与风力发电系统仿真是风能与动力工程专业的专业选修课，注重锻炼学生的数学建模和数学求解的能力。MATLAB是以数值计算和数据显示为主的软件，并包含多个学科的专业软件包，以及完善的程序开发功能。本课程要求学生掌握MATLAB的数据类型、矩阵运算、函数使用、程序编写、绘图功能以及在风力发电系统仿真中的应用。其目的是为了提高学生的分析问题和仿真系统的能力，拓展思路并为进一步深入学习提供必要的分析工具。</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="panel panel-default">
		<div class="panel-heading">The Type, Purpose and Task of This Course</div>
		<div class="panel-body">
<p>MATLAB and Wind Turbine System Simulation is specialized optional course for wind energy and power engineering major undergraduate, focusing on the exercise of students’ mathematical modeling and mathematical solving ability. MATLAB is a numerical calculation and data display software-based, and includes a multi-disciplinary professional package, and program development functions. This course requires students to master the MATLAB data type, matrix operations, the function uses, programming, graphics capabilities and wind turbine system simulation. Its purpose is to improve the ability of students to analyze problems and simulation system, to develop ideas and provide the necessary analytical tools for further study.</p>
		</div>
	</div>


	<div class="panel panel-default">
		<div class="panel-heading">教学基本要求</div>
		<div class="panel-body">
<p>使学生掌握MATLAB的使用方法及特点；掌握MATLAB基本操作；掌握矩阵运算；掌握图形绘制；掌握MATLAB程序设计的方法；能够使用MATLAB对风力发电系统进行仿真。</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="panel panel-default">
		<div class="panel-heading">Basic Teaching Requirement</div>
		<div class="panel-body">
<p>Enable students to master the use of MATLAB and characteristics, the basic operations of MATLAB, matrix operation, drawing graphics, the method of the MATLAB programming, be able to use MATLAB to simulate the wind turbine system.</p>
